---
summary: 'MXSession: The 2 initial steps (MXStore loading and events stream resume) should be performed separately'
---
assignee: manu
created: 2015-01-20 15:54:13.0
creator: gforet
description: |-
  The SDK should provide 2 distinct API to load the MXStore and resume the events stream in order to let the client handle separately this 2 steps.
  Then the client will be able to relaunch initial sync on network failure without closing MXSession instance.
